</table>

<p>
The New Testament Gateway is a comprehensive web directory of academic 
Internet resources on the New Testament. Browse or search annotated
links on everything from the Greek New Testament to Jesus in Film.
</p>
<p>
Why am I on this page?
</p>
<p>
You have followed a link to a page that does not exist, so the server
has given you this page instead (called a 404 error page). Either the
page never existed or it has been moved.
</p>
<p>
You can browse for what you are looking for on the <a href="https://web.archive.org/web/20061212151512/http://ntgateway.com/">main page</a>, or use the following search box to try to track down what you are
looking for.
